  "description": "A Resource Pack that removes borders & streaks from stained glass.",
  "body": "## Clean Stained Glass\n\nA **Resource Pack** that removes borders and streaks from stained glass, creating a clean and seamless look that’s perfect for _fog_ and _void_ effects, for example.\n\n### Compatibility\nWorks with stained glass blocks and stained glass panes. Normal (unstained) glass is not affected.\n\n**No OptiFine, CIT, or mods required.**\n\n![Black Stained Glass](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/e796b1b648e994d11f30c6d3d1e87477bd0058cc_0.webp)",
